Newcastle disease [NCD] Russia
---------------------------------
Information received on [and dated] 22 Jan 2020 from Dr. Nikolay Vlasov, Deputy Head, Federal Service for Veterinary and Phytosanitary Surveillance, Ministry of Agriculture, Moscow, Russia

Summary
Report type: Immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 9 Jan 2020
Date of confirmation of the event: 14 Jan 2020
Report date: 22 Jan 2020
Date submitted to OIE: 22 Jan 2020
Reason for notification: Recurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence: 2 Jan 2020
Manifestation of disease: Clinical disease
Causal agent: Newcastle disease virus
Nature of diagnosis: Clinical, laboratory (basic and advanced)
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country.

