Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: Unknown or inconclusive

Control measures: Movement control inside the country; surveillance within containment and/or protection zone; quarantine; official disposal of carcasses, by-products and waste; stamping out; control of wildlife reservoirs; disinfection; vaccination permitted (if a vaccine exists); no treatment of affected animals
Measures to be applied: No other measures

